#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:236
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This feature provides a lot of flexibility when defining an external tool "
#| "since all variables of the form <userinput>%{...}</userinput> are "
#| "expanded when the tool gets invoked. There are two kind of variables "
#| "supported: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para><userinput>%{variable-name}</"
